message: More work on topologyDicts and topologyGroups
Added calc_angles and calc_torsions to core.distances These are cython implementations of mass angle/torsion calculation
Added unit tests for new cython distance modules (calc_bonds  calc_angles and calc_torsions)
"a1  a2 = self.atoms[i] self.atoms[j]" changed back to "a1  a2 = self.atoms[i-1] self.atoms[j-1]"
Version bumped to 0.8.0rc3. Doc fixed and regenerated
